@10071 = ~No, we cannot.  We must not bring a Bhaalspawn here.  It would be worse than the bandits.~ [CB_74175]
@10072 = ~Ah, my good "mayor."  How good to see you once again.~
@10073 = ~You!  Why do you come here?  You are not welcome in our town!~ [CB_74177]
@10074 = ~But I will be.  To answer your question:  to give you another chance.  I wish no violence.  You know that.  We can settle this in other, more civilized ways.~
