Launcher:  Bow~
@20428 = ~Arrows of Stunning~
@20429 = ~The Arrow of Stunning looks like any other normal arrow other than the fact that it seems to pulse slightly when notched on a bowstring.  The true effects can be seen when one strikes an opponent and they fall to the ground stunned.

