@20443 = ~Amulet of Dark Flesh~
@20444 = ~A horrible cursed item crafted by the Calishite necromancer Niri Eddin, the Amulet of Dark Flesh is a token of disease and slow death.  Eddin gave the item to his secret enemies as gifts and reclaimed it through his thief servants when the sickness had run its course.  Niri is believed to still be "alive" somewhere in the realms, despite the fact that he was a human born in 832 DR.

