@20456 = ~Boots of Moander~
@20457 = ~These patchwork boots of red and black leather were created by cultists of Moander, an ancient god of rot and decay.  The boots were used by a number of the Darkbringer's faithful when they fought against Moander's numerous foes, many of whom worshipped nature deities.  The boots were last claimed by Aldarra of Chauntea, who in turn gave them to a half-elven ranger friend, Liberon Twelvetrees.

