@20477 = ~These arrows are known less for their damaging power than they are for their annoying summoning power.  Invented by a black-hearted gnome named Turbar Talinbar, the Goblin Arrows are commonly found in the quivers of mischievous halflings and elves.  Several adventuring companies use the Goblin Arrows before launching any major attacks.

