@20486 = ~Holdfast Arrows~
@20487 = ~Employed almost exclusively by Eldathyn rangers in the western heartlands of Faerun, Holdfast Arrows are prized for their ability to subdue a target with little harm.  The arrows are commonly used on rampaging animals but are quite effective against malicious humanoids.  They are typically adorned with blue and green ribbons and flowers to show that they were created by the peacekeepers of Eldath.  This makes them somewhat less effective in combat.

