@20612 = ~Foot Locker~
@20613 = ~The Soubar Major gave you this bag to put all your personal belongings in.  If you do not place ALL your stuff in the bag, it may get lost.  The bag will be returned to you once you become a commissioned officer, but while enlisted, you must wear the uniform of the Soubar Guard.  When you've got all your stuff in the bag, give it to the Major.~
@20614 = ~This letter is addressed to High Merchant Logan Coprith in Trademeet.  You are to deliver it to him for the Major of Soubar.

Greetings to an old friend-

Well met, Logan.  I apologize for the briefness of this missive, but I am in dire need of any assistance you can provide my home town and the region itself.  As I explained in my last letter to you, the region has suffered greatly at the hands of a renegade half-orc by the name of Sureblade.  His bandit legions have sacked the nearby village of Triel, and are attempting conquest of Soubar.  We are in desperate straights, and cannot hold against them for long.  Please, Logan, if you can spare any men, supplies, or financing, I would be in your debt.  

May Helm watch over you-

(the signature is scribbled and you cannot make out the name)
Major of Soubar

Post-Script:  Sabby sends her love to you and yours.~
