@20688 = ~Sureblade's Journal~
@20689 = ~The rough and quick strokes of a heavy-handed writer line the pages of this book with descriptive images of violence and destruction.  A number of the past few entries reveal what you know of Sureblade's activities; the orders he issued to attack Soubar, the surrounding farms, and earlier entries tell of the conquest of Triel.  There is nothing that you can see in the journal that you already do not know of, and you drop it in your pack as evidence.~
@20690 = ~The rough and quick strokes of a heavy-handed writer line the pages of this book with descriptive images of violence and destruction.  A number of the past few entries reveal what you know of Sureblade's activities; the orders he issued to attack Soubar, the surrounding farms, and earlier entries tell of the conquest of Triel.  

One entry does, however, catch your attention.  It is undated, but as there is not much writing after the entry, it was written fairly recently:

"The innkeep I bought served his purpose well enough, though I am not happy about his dealings with the Bhaalspawn.  He should not have been exposed by the One, and has paid for his failure.  The fact that he was exposed has forced me to take drastic measures against Soubar, sooner than I had desired, and I expect that by the end of the season, the entire region will finally be under my control."

There is nothing else that you can see in the journal that you already do not know of, and you drop it in your pack as evidence.~
