@20806 = ~SELENCE grew up on the city streets of Athkatla, which was not the most appropriate place for a young girl.  Selence never really had the chance to be a child.  Her circumstances of being a young street thug may not have been the most pleasant, but she'll never admit that she secretly wishes her life could have been different.  As it is, Selence has become quite a thief, and hopes to eventually run an underground network of spies, smugglers, and robbers.  Selence has a plan, which is more than most others in Faerûn can admit to, and she will do all that she can to make her dreams come true, even if her dreams are not the most ethical of dreams.~

































